## Pipeline Summary

### Pre-commit (automatic, every commit)

```
git commit
  ├── lint-staged (Prettier + ESLint on staged files) ... ~2-5s
  ├── tsc --noEmit (TypeScript check) .................. ~3-10s
  ├── trivy fs --scanners secret (secret scan) ......... ~1-3s
  └── pnpm test (unit tests) ........................... ~5-15s
```

### Manual commands (run when needed)

```bash
pnpm security:deps    # Scan dependencies for vulnerabilities
pnpm security         # Full security scan (secrets + deps)
pnpm check            # Full quality check (lint + types + test + secrets)
```

### Cursor Agent (automatic via MCP, while editing)

```
After file edit:
  ├── CodeScene code_health_score ...................... automatic
  ├── If score < 6.0 → alert user
  └── If score < 4.0 → offer auto-refactor

Before commit (when agent commits):
  └── CodeScene pre_commit_code_health_safeguard ....... all staged files
```

