## Adapting for different project types

### Python projects

Replace lint-staged config:

```json
{
  "*.py": ["black", "isort", "flake8"]
}
```

Pre-commit hook:

```bash
#!/bin/sh
npx lint-staged
trivy fs --scanners secret --exit-code 1 --severity HIGH,CRITICAL .
python -m pytest --tb=short -q
```

### Monorepo (Turborepo/Nx)

```bash
#!/bin/sh
npx lint-staged
npx turbo typecheck --filter=[HEAD^1]
trivy fs --scanners secret --exit-code 1 --severity HIGH,CRITICAL .
npx turbo test --filter=[HEAD^1]
```

